0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0623\u064e\u064a\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0635\u064f\u0648\u0645\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37804,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/05\/20\/kab-intending-sin-after-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":18951,"position":3},"title":"Ka\u2019b on Ramadan: Whoever fasts intending to sin after Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 20, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Rajab reported: Ka\u2019b ibn Malik, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWhoever fasts the month of Ramadan and he says to himself that he will return to sinful disobedience when Ramadan is over, his fasting is rejected.\u201d Source: Lat\u0323a\u0304\u2019if al-Ma\u2019a\u0304rif 1\/222 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0631\u062c\u0628 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0628\u0652 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5468,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/21\/ramadan-make-up-missed-sawm\/","url_meta":{"origin":18951,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Making up missed fasts throughout the year","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Salamah reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \u201cI had to make up some fasts I missed during the month of Ramadan, but I was unable to do so until the month of Sha\u2019ban as\u00a0I was busy with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19450,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/07\/03\/fasting-ramadan-three-days\/","url_meta":{"origin":18951,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Fasting Ramadan, three days a month","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 3, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFasting the month of patience, which is Ramadan, and three days from every month is like fasting the entire year.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 2408 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/p